      <div class="span4 offset1" style="margin-top:20px">
        <a href="<%= offices_path %>" style="text-decoration:none;">
          <button class="btn btn-large btn-primary btn-call-to-action input-block-level"> See Listings </button>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row" style="padding-top:10px; background-color: #ffffff; margin-right: -20px; padding-bottom:   40px;">
    <div class="span12">
      <h2>Why search on Tradewinz?</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="row" style="margin-left: 0;">
      <div class="span6">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span1"> <%= image_tag("icon-free.png", alt: "icon free") %></div>
          <div class="span5">
            <h4>No fees</h4>
            You get 100% of the rent. We are doing this to support small businesses in the USA. We succeed when you succeed.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span1"> <%= image_tag("icon-time.png", alt: "icon screen") %>
          </div>
          <div class="span5">
            <h4>Save time</h4>
            We recruit and screen local, reliable applicants for you, many of whom are like-minded entrepreneurs you may enjoy meeting.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row" style="margin-top: 24px; margin-left: 0;">
      <div class="span6">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span1"> <%= image_tag("icon-trusted.png", alt: "icon free") %>
          </div>
          <div class="span5">
            <h4>Trusted brand</h4>
            From the makers of Quickbooks and Turbo Tax - over 6M small businesses trust us to help with their finances.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span1"> <%= image_tag("icon-unite.png", alt: "icon free") %>
          </div>
          <div class="span5">
            <h4>By and for small business</h4>
            You contact information is private, you approve who can see it. You'll also get metrics to track how much interest your listing generates.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div> <!-- /container -->

<!-- Modal -->
<div id="rentModal" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="rentModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
    <h3 id="rentModalLabel">Studio Rental Guide</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <p>Find below the average rentals in different cities:</p>
    <table class="table table-striped">
      <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>New York</th>
        <th>Los Angeles</th>
      </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>$55 - $75 an hour</td>
        <td>$35 - $60 an hour</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>$200 - $300 /half day (4-5 hrs) </td>
        <td>$200 - $250 /half day (4-5 hrs)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>$400 - $900 /full day (8-12 hrs) </td>
        <td>$450 – $600 /full day (8-12 hrs) </td>
      </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <table class="table table-striped">
      <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Chicago</th>
        <th>San Francisco</th>
      </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>$55 - $75 an hour</td>
        <td>$35 - $60 an hour</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>$200 - $300 /half day (4-5 hrs) </td>
        <td>$200 - $250 /half day (4-5 hrs)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>$400 - $900 /full day (8-12 hrs) </td>
        <td>$450 – $600 /full day (8-12 hrs) </td>
      </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p> Providing the following amenities may increase your rental rates:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Location – downtowns, with their easy access via public transport, are more expensive than suburbs.</li>
      <li>Equipment + accessories – Studio rentals that come with lights, umbrellas, veils, accessories and other specialized equipment rentals cost more.</li>
      <li>Higher ceiling.</li>
      <li>Freight elevators</li>
      <li>Basic refreshments and water</li>
      <li>Separate make-up room, dressing room and waiting areas.</li>
      <li>Storage</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Close</button>
  </div>
</div>
